Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Over The Top{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Separated from Sanji and the others,\NLuffy arrived on the Land of Wano alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and saved Otama from Kaido's soldiers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to know if this is \Nthe Land of Wano or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a region called Kuri\Nin the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro! Big Bro! Big Bro!\NBig Bro! Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:03:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro? Why do you call me "Big Bro"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you saved my life,\Nyou're my Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"He'll Come!\NThe Legend of Ace in the Land of Wano!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you being chased?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the town for shopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But on my way home,\Nthat evil one's men with the baboon found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect me, Komachiyo \Nattacked the baboon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that's why you guys were in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They stole everything I bought!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of anger,\NI said something that goes against the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Kozuki Clan comes back,\Nthey'll teach you a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd never be able to go home again,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but thanks to you, I got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let me return the favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that'll help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just arrived here so I \Nhave a lot of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! You need to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is this okay?\N--Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy won't find it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! As I thought,\Nthere's nothing to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to invite you over for a treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:39.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,KOMACHIYO - A LION-DOG
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro! Hihimaru! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:42.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,HIHIMARU - A NEW FRIEND
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Hihimaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just came up with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm counting on you, Hihimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are pirates that I like\Nand that I don't like!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes no difference to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong and kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My house is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a village in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's gone, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, my Master-{\i1}sama{\i0} and I live by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the future, I'm gonna be a bewitching...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...female ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bewitching"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, "bewitching"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's "bewitching"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dirty, small, and stinky here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro, that's a little impolite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, smells delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be ready soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it ready yet, Tama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freshly-cooked rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you gonna eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't become a ninja if I'm not agile!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seconds, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was all I cooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no more pickles, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just joking when I asked for seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bad at lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had enough yet\Nbut she's kind enough to cook for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so nice! Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you lying down here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you ate the rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did. Who are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making noise, stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't becoming of a samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just here because Tama cooked for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did she cook for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many days do you think it's been\Nsince she ate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she busily weaves hats every day\Nand sells them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can only earn barely enough for\None person to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes we get to eat barnyard grass\Nand that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at least, twice a year,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on her birthday and New Year's,\NI want her to eat rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:52.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,RICE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I gave her money today
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sent her to the town\Nto buy rice for her eighth birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you eat that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me for cooking it\Nwithout asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He saved my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring disgrace on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll weave many hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me return the favor to\NBig Bro Luffy properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must've done a foolish thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose she drank the river water\Nto ease her hunger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,River waters in this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are polluted by liquid wastes\Nfrom Kaido's factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a small girl like her,\Nit's like drinking poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why are you living here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are places that would be\Na bit better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's waiting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone who promised to come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a pirate named Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ace that you're waiting for is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Portgas D. Ace, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro, you're a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She fainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Ace visited the Land of Wano, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a devil or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you tell Otama\Nthat Ace died so casually?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's true,\Nthat wasn't the right time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how long she waits,\NAce won't come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should've considered\Nwhen and how to say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no delicacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy.\NI'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're a pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I generally don't like pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hitetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:25.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,TENGUYAMA HITETSU - A SWORDSMITH
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a swordsmith.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:28.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,TENGUYAMA HITETSU - A SWORDSMITH\N(A BEAUTIFUL GIRL KOKESHI DOLL COLLECTOR)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace is now gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Tama and move to a better place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I truly want to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've been waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for someone here for a long time myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only the two of us here now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there was a village \Ncalled Amigasa before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But around a year ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:19:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a man who joined Kaido's army as a Headliner\Ncame here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a pirate named X. Drake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The village's five key samurai\Nwere taken down
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and everything was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the Land of Wano,\Nthere is only one place that's thriving now
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that is the Flower Capital\Nwhere the Shogun Orochi lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other places...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...were turned into lawless wilderness areas\Nby Kaido and his clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man came here four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This village was always poor
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:20:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and no one had enough to live on\Nso people often died of hunger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when we thought that \Nthe village was doomed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ace was tossed up on the beach.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The villagers stole all the food and water...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...from those weak pirates{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then ate it up and stayed alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ace watched them finish everything,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then, surprisingly,\Nhe easily untied himself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone thought he was gonna retaliate\Nand prepared themselves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you eat enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you want something sweet now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where can I find something for dessert?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm gonna go pick it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone was stunned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ace stayed at the village\Nfor several weeks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Otama was especially attached to him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe our lives were saved\Nby the shipwrecked pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.57,0:22:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The communication was\Nprobably cut at Kuri Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that they \Nwere beaten by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.15,0:22:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know how many there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there is no ship, but it's definite\Nthat they came from the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.22,0:22:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell Kaido-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.70,0:23:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and Hancock get in \Na fierce fight against
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the army of the world's \Nstrongest bounty hunter!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Side Story! The World's \NGreatest Bounty Hunter, Cidre!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.36,0:23:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Pirates Fest!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King of the Pirates challenges you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:37.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,TO GET THE KING OF THE PIRATES' TREASURE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on and seize the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:39.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ALL THE PIRATES AND MARINES COME TOGETHER!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The movie ONE PIECE STAMPEDE!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.04,0:23:45.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,AND... A DARK PLOT IS LAUNCHED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.19,0:23:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ambition...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is ignited!
